<ol>
  <li>使用Google Cloud网页版ssh，切换到root
    <div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">sudo</span> <span class="nt">-i</span>  
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>编辑ssh配置文件
    <div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config  
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>修改以下的内容
    <div class="language-shell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>PermitRootLogin <span class="nb">yes
</span>PasswordAuthentication <span class="nb">yes</span>
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>
